  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to determine the frequency of Lysosomal Acid Lipase Deficiency
      (LAL D) by lysosomal acid lipase (LAL) enzyme activity assay in patients who are considered
      to be at risk.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
