    <measure>LAL D frequency based on LAL enzyme assay.</measure>
    <time_frame>approximately 1 month</time_frame>
    <description>The endpoint of this study is the frequency of LAL D in at-risk patients, based on results from the LAL enzyme assay.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
